                  <collation>
                    <p>The quires, signed with letters, were originally upwards of 20 in number</p>
                  </collation>
                  <condition>
                    <list>
                      <item>
                        <p>A few leaves are much stained and slightly torn, especially <locus>foll. 9</locus>, <locus>60</locus>, <locus>93</locus>, and <locus>94</locus>.</p>
                      </item>
                      <item>
                        <p>Several quires have been lost, both at the beginning and end, and some of the remainder are imperfect, leaves being missing after <locus>foll. 8</locus>, <locus>53</locus>, <locus>54</locus>, <locus>58</locus>, <locus>60</locus>, <locus>62</locus>, <locus>73</locus>, <locus>79</locus>, <locus>92</locus>, <locus>94</locus>, and <locus>95</locus></p>
